        "timestamp": "2022-02-16 12:32:38.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis review is part of POLICY-3896 - Apex Editor using Spring Boot.\nIt was necessary to do some restructuring of Apex Editor to facilitate migration to Spring Boot. Also, as part of POLICY-3638 (Run all GUIs in same jar), it will be necessary to break Apex Editor into separate frontend and backend modules. I am thus restructuring the frontend build here to reduce the complexity of further reviews.\nAs a bonus, the restructure simplifies the POM and fixes an issue where JS source and test files got copied to the JAR.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
